<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="shine-v">shine <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ʃaɪn/    美 /ʃaɪn/  </p>
<p>(shone, shone)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vi-vt">1.★ <strong>vi &amp; vt (使) 发光；(使) 发亮；照耀：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The <strong>moon shone</strong> brightly in the sky.
皓月当空。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please shine your flashlight over there.
请把手电筒往那儿照。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>shiny /'ʃaɪni/ adj   </p></div>